This function provides TransponderID data over CAN to SAM during Key Learning process

The function is called sequentially for all 8 key slots during Key Learning process and only after evaluation of the Learning Crypts received from WFS is successful. Based on the key number (i.e., key slot in range 0..7), the function sends the TransponderID data to SAM over CAN. The TransponderID data bytes are sent in reverted order.
